      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. the formula makes sense. but like, what are some specific ways i can tell if my stock is just sitting there too long vs just being part of a normal seasonal cycle? i feel like i have a lot of stuff just piling up in the back room and it's hard to tell if it's a real problem or not.",
